  supersededBy[0]:
  conflictsWith[0]:
  sections[5]{title,body}:
    Vision,Demonstrate the library with an end-to-end example usable as a reference for agents and developers.
    Objectives,Show a React TypeScript todo manager while enforcing structured docs for requirements and design.
    NonGoals,No backend service and no authentication are included in this example; external integrations remain out-of-scope.
    Success Indicators,Users can run the app locally run docs checks and generation and map decisions to artifacts.
    Rollout Steps,Create source docs first then wire UI implementation with checks and package validation.
